I '''Anne Rice'''<ref name=Bowman>{{cite book|last=Bowman|first=John S.|title=The Cambridge Dictionary of American Biography|year=1995|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=New York|isbn=0-521-40258-1|page=607}}</ref> (mibait '''Howard Allen Frances O'Brien'''; Octubre 4, 1941 - 2021) metung yang  Americanang talasulat ning [[gothic fiction]], [[kasulatang Cristianu]], ampong [[erotica]]. Mapalyaring pikabalwan yang dili ing kayang sikat ampong maimpluwensyang serye da reng nobela, ing ''[[The Vampire Chronicles]]'', a dudurut king manimunang tauan, i [[Lestat de Lioncourt|Lestat]]. Gewa ra nong pelikula deng adwang libru king ''The Vampire Chronicles'', ing ''[[Interview with the Vampire: The Vampire Chronicles]]'' anyang 1994, ampo ing ''[[Queen of the Damned (film)|Queen of the Damned]]'' in 2002.

Meragul ya king New Orleans i Rice, nung nu ya menuknangan anyang kayang kayanakan, bayu ya minalis king Texas, at kaybat king [[San Francisco]]. Meragul ya king metung a relihyosung pamilyang Katoliku, oneng megi yang ateista anyang kayanakan yang atsu king idad. Migumpisa ing kayang karerang propesyonal king pamanyulat anyang milimbag ya ing ''Interview with the Vampire'' anyang 1976, kabang manuknangan ya king California, at megumpisa yang sinulat katuglung na niti anyang dekadang 1980s. Kanitang kalibudtang ning 2000s, kaybat ning kayang pikabalwan a pamanyubli king Katolisismu, linimbag nong Rice deng nobelang ''[[Christ the Lord: Out of Egypt]]'' ampong ''[[Christ the Lord: The Road to Cana]]'', kwentung gewang piksyon da reng insidenti king bye nang [[Jesus]]. Pilang banwa kaybat, dinistansya ya king organisadung Kristyanismu, uling king e na pamanayun king pusisyun ning Pisamban kareng isyung pang-sosyedad, oneng pangaku nang makasentru ya pa murin ing kayang bye king kasalpantayanan king Dios. 

Maygit nong 100 milyung kopya da reng libru nang Rice ing misali, at uli na niti, metung ya kareng pekasikat a talasulat a Americanu king bayung kasalesayang Americanu.<ref name=Fantastic>{{cite web|title=Anne Rice|url=http://www.fantasticfiction.co.uk/r/anne-rice/|publisher=FantasticFiction|accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref><ref name="On Conversion">{{cite web|title=PreachingToday.com & Christianity Today|url=http://www.preachingtoday.com/illustrations/2008/march/10032408.html|publisher=PreachingToday.com & Christianity Today|accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref> Lipat ning misamut ing reaksyun kareng mumuna nang obra, sinikat ya kareng kayang kritiku anyang dekadang 1980s. Malalam dong inanalisa deng istilu nang pamanyulat ampo ing kalamnan nang pangliteratura deng obra na deng komentarista king literatura. Asawa ne kilub ning 41 banwa ing poeta ampong pintor a i [[Stan Rice]] manibat 1961 anggang mete ya king kanser king utak anyang 2002 king idad a 60.<ref name=Phone>{{cite web|last=Rice|first=Anne|title=Phone Message Transcript: December 9, 2002|url=http://www.annerice.com/ph20021209.htm|publisher=Anne Rice|work=AnneRice.com|accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref><ref name="Stan Obit">{{cite web|title=Stan Rice Obituary|url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/nytimes/obituary.aspx?n=stan-rice&pid=646671&fhid=2618|publisher=Legacy.com|accessdate=10 June 2012}}</ref> Adwa la anak Stan, i  Michele, a mete king [[leukemia]] king idad a limang banwa, ampo i [[Christopher Rice|Christopher]], a metung mu namang talasulat.

Bukud kareng nobela nang tungkul kareng bampira, sinulat ya mu naman aliwang libru i Rice anti ing  ''[[The Feast of All Saints (novel)|The Feast of All Saints]]'' (mipalage king telebisyun anyang 2001) ampo ing ''[[Servant of the Bones]]'', nung nu ya mibasi ing 2011 a seryeng pangkomiks.  Megawa la mu namang komiks deng mapilang libru ning ''The Vampire Chronicles'' kapamilatan da reng aliwang talalimbag. Sinulat ya mu namang erotic fiction i Rice lalam ning talipampan a Anne Rampling ampong A.&nbsp;N.&nbsp;Roquelaure, kayabe ya ing ''[[Exit to Eden]]'', a megawang pelikula ing [[Exit to Eden (pelikula)|pelikulang 1994]].

